Title : Kapella River
Text : The '''Kapella River''' is a [[river]] in the [[Kitimat Ranges]] of the [[Coast Mountains]] in [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]].  It rises west of [[Cornice Peak (Kitimat Ranges)|Cornice Peak]] and flows northwest to join the [[Kitlope River]].<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/3026.html BCNames/GeoBC entry "Kapella River"]</ref>

